zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527460\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527460\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 02, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fdp1665702576817.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fdp1665702576817.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fdp1665702576817.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fdp1665702576817\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">validatekey \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__validatekey_246518\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Validate a key of the current occurrence.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__topic_d78953e1_d78954e1_d78955e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104fdp1665702576817_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__codeblock_qfc_lyy_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">validatekey  Entity  {,KeyNumber}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__section_w2587ab1b7b5_w2588ab1b7_w2589ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__p_d78959e1_d78960e1_d78961e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">validatekey \"MYENT\", 1</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__topic_d51917e1_d51918e1_d51919e1_d51920e1_d51921e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d553332e75\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__table_d7712e1_d7713e1_d7714e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__table_d7712e1_d7713e1_d7714e1__entry__1\">Parameter </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__table_d7712e1_d7713e1_d7714e1__entry__2\"> DataType </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__table_d7712e1_d7713e1_d7714e1__entry__3\">Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fdp1665702576817__table_d7712e1_d7713e1_d7714e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fdp1665702576817__table_d7712e1_d7713e1_d7714e1__entry__2\">String </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fdp1665702576817__table_d7712e1_d7713e1_d7714e1__entry__3\">Entity in which a key is to be validated. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fdp1665702576817__table_d7712e1_d7713e1_d7714e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumber</var></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fdp1665702576817__table_d7712e1_d7713e1_d7714e1__entry__2\">Number </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fdp1665702576817__table_d7712e1_d7713e1_d7714e1__entry__3\">Key that is to be located (as defined for\n                           <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>; whole (integer) number; the value will be\n                        truncated to form an integer. <p class=\"p\">If omitted, the default value of\n                              <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">1</span> (the primary key) is chosen. Higher\n                              <var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumbers</var> (2, 3, 4, and so on) identify a\n                           candidate key depending upon your model definition. Indexes are not\n                           allowed.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__topic_d51922e1_d51923e1_d51924e1_d51925e1_d51926e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d553332e154\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__table_d7427e1_d7428e1_d7429e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__table_d7427e1_d7428e1_d7429e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__table_d7427e1_d7428e1_d7429e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fdp1665702576817__table_d7427e1_d7428e1_d7429e1__entry__1\">&lt;0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fdp1665702576817__table_d7427e1_d7428e1_d7429e1__entry__2\">An error occurred.\n\t\t\t\t <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fdp1665702576817__table_d7427e1_d7428e1_d7429e1__entry__1\">&gt;=0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fdp1665702576817__table_d7427e1_d7428e1_d7429e1__entry__2\">Statement executed successfully.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__topic_d51932e1_d51933e1_d51934e1_d51935e1_d51936e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d553332e213\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__d6417e20\">Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__topic_d51937e1_d51938e1_d51939e1_d51940e1_d51941e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d553332e222\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__p_d78986e1_d78987e1_d78988e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">validatekey</span> statement validates\n            the specified key of the current occurrence of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>. If any field\n            of the key is marked as modified and has not been successfully validated, the necessary\n            field-level validate triggers and the validatekey trigger are activated. For more\n            information, see the \"Validate\" topic.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__p_d78989e1_d78990e1_d78991e1\">As each field of the key is successfully validated,\n            the corresponding validation flag (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldvalidation</span>) is set to 0.\n            When the entire key is successfully validated, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keyvalidation</span> is set\n            to 0.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__note_w2590ab1b7c15b7_w2591ab1b7c15_w2592ab1b7_w2593ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Validation statements\n        (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">validatefield</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">validatekey</span>,\n        <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">validateocc</span>, and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">validate</span>) activate the validation\n      triggers such as validate and validatekey. You should therefore be careful when using these\n      statements in validation triggers.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__section_hbq_vyy_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d553332e261\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">validatekey</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following operation validates a new primary key that it receives as\n            an argument:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104fdp1665702576817_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"fdp1665702576817__codeblock_gt4_xyy_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation NEWKEYCHECK\nparams\n string NEWKEY : IN\n boolean OK : OUT\nendparams\nPK1.MYENT = NEWKEY\nvalidatekey \"MYENT\", 1\nif ($status = 0)\n OK = &lt;TRUE&gt;\nelse\n OK = &lt;FALSE&gt;\nendif\nend; NEWKEYCHECK</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrk1665702576500.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Validate</a><p>Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jwi1665702576586.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validatefield</a><p>Validate a field of the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bwv1665702576896.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validateocc</a><p>Validate an occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jqe1665702576424.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$dataerrorcontext</a><p>Return the context of the last validation error.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/opq1665702649630.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$procerrorcontext</a><p>Return the location of the error specified by $procerror.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wcw1719485700746.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keyvalidation</a><p>Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qdc1665702602510.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldvalidation</a><p>Identify whether a field requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ugh1665703129789.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger validate (Field)</a><p>System trigger that defines the procedural checks to validate a modified field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/frh1665703129863.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger validateKey</a><p>System trigger that defines the procedural checks to validate a modified primary or candidate key.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iwi1665702603846.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger validate (Entity)</a><p>System trigger for validating entity occurrences.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527460\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527460\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "validatekey Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 02, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 validatekey Validate a key of the current occurrence. Explain this code validatekey Entity {,KeyNumber} Copy Example: validatekey \"MYENT\", 1 Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter DataType Description Entity String Entity in which a key is to be validated. KeyNumber Number Key that is to be located (as defined for Entity ; whole (integer) number; the value will be truncated to form an integer. If omitted, the default value of 1 (the primary key) is chosen. Higher KeyNumbers (2, 3, 4, and so on) identify a candidate key depending upon your model definition. Indexes are not allowed. Return Values Table 2. Values returned in $status Value Meaning <0 An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. >=0 Statement executed successfully. Use Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports. Description The validatekey statement validates the specified key of the current occurrence of Entity . If any field of the key is marked as modified and has not been successfully validated, the necessary field-level validate triggers and the validatekey trigger are activated. For more information, see the \"Validate\" topic. As each field of the key is successfully validated, the corresponding validation flag ( $fieldvalidation ) is set to 0. When the entire key is successfully validated, $keyvalidation is set to 0. Note: Validation statements ( validatefield , validatekey , validateocc , and validate ) activate the validation triggers such as validate and validatekey. You should therefore be careful when using these statements in validation triggers. Example: Using validatekey The following operation validates a new primary key that it receives as an argument: Explain this code operation NEWKEYCHECK params string NEWKEY : IN boolean OK : OUT endparams PK1.MYENT = NEWKEY validatekey \"MYENT\", 1 if ($status = 0) OK = <TRUE> else OK = <FALSE> endif end; NEWKEYCHECK Copy Related Links Validate Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default). validatefield Validate a field of the current occurrence. validateocc Validate an occurrence. $dataerrorcontext Return the context of the last validation error. $procerrorcontext Return the location of the error specified by $procerror. $keyvalidation Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation. $fieldvalidation Identify whether a field requires validation. trigger validate (Field) System trigger that defines the procedural checks to validate a modified field. trigger validateKey System trigger that defines the procedural checks to validate a modified primary or candidate key. trigger validate (Entity) System trigger for validating entity occurrences. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}